# Section heading
## Subsection

Formatting:  *italics*,
**bold**, super^script^,
sub~script~, ~~strikeout~~.
A line break can be forced  
with two spaces  
at the end of the line.

> Indented quotation

Links:
[ext](http://google.com),
[Wiki Link](),
![image](/img/banner.png),
[heading](#section-heading).

Indented code block:

    #include <stdbool.h>

Or a delimited code block:

~~~ { .haskell }
let a = 1:a in head a
~~~

- bulleted
- list

* * * * *

1.  ordered
2.  list
    a. sublist (indent 4 sp)
    b. another
3.  item three

term
:   definition
orange
:   orange fruit

